  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18-65

          -  Moderate or severe major depression with duration of a minimum of two years OR
             &quot;double depression&quot; (dysthymia and moderate/severe major depression simultaneously)
             OR moderate or severe major depression with duration of a minimum of two years, only
             partially remitted during the time period

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Psychotic disorder

          -  Bipolar disorder

          -  Current substance abuse (excluding nicotine)
      </textblock>
